    <section class="section">
        <h2>Key Services</h2>
        <div class="services">
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Market Entry Advisory</h3>
                <p>Strategic planning for entering Mexico's manufacturing hubs, including market analysis, competitor benchmarking, and nearshoring strategies to leverage USMCA benefits.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Legal and Regulatory Compliance</h3>
                <p>Assistance with IMMEX certification, permits, licenses, and compliance with Mexican labor, environmental, and trade regulations, similar to services provided by Co-Production International.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Site Selection and Facility Setup</h3>
                <p>Identifying optimal locations in industrial parks (e.g., Monterrey or Querétaro), facility design, and setup for automation lines, including robotics and IoT integration.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Supply Chain and Logistics Optimization</h3>
                <p>Building regional supply chains, supplier mapping, and logistics partnerships to reduce costs and improve efficiency, inspired by Onilog Group's approach.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Venture Capital and Equity Partnerships</h3>
                <p>Providing funding as shareholders or venture capitalists, with equity stakes in joint ventures for automation tech firms, focusing on milestones like production scaling.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Talent Recruitment and Training</h3>
                <p>Sourcing skilled engineers and technicians for industrial automation, with training programs in PLCs, SCADA, and cobots, addressing Mexico's growing talent pool.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Distribution Channel Development</h3>
                <p>Establishing new sales and distribution networks through local partnerships, targeting sectors like automotive and electronics.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Automation Integration Services</h3>
                <p>Expert support for implementing Industry 4.0 solutions, including cobots, predictive maintenance AI, and IoT systems, drawing from Innovative Automation's global expertise.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
